## ‚úÖ Best Practices

### Do's

- ‚úÖ Use consistent spacing from the spacing system
- ‚úÖ Apply appropriate typography hierarchy
- ‚úÖ Maintain card-based layouts for organization
- ‚úÖ Use dark cards for featured/important content
- ‚úÖ Include empty states with helpful messaging
- ‚úÖ Apply subtle shadows for depth perception
- ‚úÖ Ensure sufficient color contrast for readability

### Don'ts

- ‚ùå Mix custom spacing values with system values
- ‚ùå Use more than 3 typography weights in one screen
- ‚ùå Create cards without padding or with inconsistent padding
- ‚ùå Use bright colors for large background areas
- ‚ùå Skip empty states for data-dependent sections
- ‚ùå Apply heavy shadows to small elements
- ‚ùå Use low-contrast text colors that are hard to read

